"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-27-divers-shower-every-jump-olympic-diving-questions-answered-21259417\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ever wondered why divers shower when they come out of the pool?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 18, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 62}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or perhaps you are confused by the tiny towels they use, or the tape they wear.\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tiny towels\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 110}, {\"ngram\": \"the tape\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheParis 2024 Olympicsare firmly underway and for those not lucky enough to hold a ticket to an event in the city of love, it's time to settle in front of the TV and watchTeam GBgo for gold.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheParis 2024 Olympicsare\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 170}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"the TV\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the diving, our best hopes are pinned onTom Daleyand Jack Laugher towin medals for Great Britain, but while we will be crossing our fingers that they come away with the crown, you may also notice that there are a couple of unusual traditions in the sport.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jack Laugher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9885728636084576, \"rank\": 0.0064337634775926186, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the diving\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"our best hopes\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"our fingers\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"the crown\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"unusual traditions\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest updates on the 2024 Olympic Games For instance, why do divers shower after every jump, and why do they use those small towels?\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"latest updates\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"every jump\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"those small towels\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might also have noticed that many divers wear tape and, for some reason, water is sprayed over the diving pool.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many divers\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"tape\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"some reason\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"the diving pool\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are eight Olympic diving events, divided equally between the three-metre springboard and 10-metre platform.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight Olympic diving events\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-metre springboard\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"10-metre platform\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes compete in individual and synchronized contests from both.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"contests\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their dives are rated by a panel of judges, who assess the complexity (how hard it is) and how well it is executed.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their dives\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"a panel\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the complexity\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eleven judges score competitors on a range of factors, with thescores added together and then multiplied by the degree of difficulty for each individual dive.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eleven\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"score competitors\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"factors\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"thescores\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the degree\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"each individual dive\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That also includes how smoothly divers enter the water when they land.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In synchronized events, divers have the added pressure of being judged on how well they mirror their partner.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"synchronized events\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the added pressure\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"their partner\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All synchronized diving events consist of one roundwith eight teams.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All synchronized diving events\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"one roundwith eight teams\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each team will do six dives.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each team\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"six dives\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Divers shower after each dive in order to keep their muscles warm and loose.This helps to avoid injuries while competing.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Divers\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"each dive\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"their muscles\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, between dives the competitors often keep themselves warm and relaxed in a hot tub.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"a hot tub\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The air on the pool deck is often cool - and the divers will feel this more keenly when they are wet - so it's important they keep warm.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The air\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool deck\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"the divers\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shower helps with this.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The shower\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they do not, the cold may cause them to tense up and, even if it's only slight, this can affect their performance when they dive and potentially lead to injury.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cold\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Water is sprayed on diving pools to help athletes see the surfaceand judge how far they are from the water.\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Water\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"diving pools\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The water disrupts the surface, which would otherwise remain still, so the divers can judge the angle they will be hitting the pool at - something which is crucial for their safety.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"the divers\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the angle\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"their safety\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Underneath the water, a device known as a 'bubbler' is installed on the pool floor to provide a compressed air cushion of bubbles, which protects the divers from injury.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"a device\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'bubbler\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool floor\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"a compressed air cushion\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"bubbles\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"the divers\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Divers wear tape to relieve pain in their muscles and joints, and for added support.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Divers\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"tape\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"their muscles\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"joints\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"added support\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The acrobatic sequences that divers perform put a lot of stress on the body, so, again, the tape helps prevent injury and avoid any muscle movement that might hinder performance.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The acrobatic sequences\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2784}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"the tape\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"any muscle movement\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not just any old tape, however.\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just any old tape\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Called Kinesio (also referred to as 'K tape'), it was developed in Japan in the 70s by chiropractor Dr Kenso Kase, and is popular with athletes across many other sports - proving especially popular with swimmers too.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9344498860625144, \"rank\": 0.07014727998401016, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenzo_Suzuki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenso\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenzo_Suzuki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenzo_Suzuki\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kinesio\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"K tape\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"the 70s\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it's said to reduce swelling and allow fluid to move through the body more smoothly, some scientists have suggested it may have little more than a placebo effect.\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fluid\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"some scientists\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"a placebo effect\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simply put, divers use those little towels to keep dry.Known as Chamois towels, they are extremely water absorbent, allowing divers to dry off quickly.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3390, \"end\": 3397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chamois_leather\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.4355030509875608e-12, \"text\": \"Chamois\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chamois_leather\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chamois_leather\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"those little towels\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3368}, {\"ngram\": \"extremely water absorbent\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3440}, {\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Towelling off before a dive is important, because the athletes do not want to risk slipping while gripping onto their legs during a tuck or pike.\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dive\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"their legs\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3601}, {\"ngram\": \"a tuck\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"pike\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only would this hinder their performance, it can also be dangerous.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An added benefit of these towels is that they are very easy to wring out.\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An added benefit\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3714}, {\"ngram\": \"these towels\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You may sometimes see divers dropping little towels into the pool from the diving platform.\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3801}, {\"ngram\": \"little towels\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3824}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"the diving platform\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This helps them judge the distance they are about to dive from.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pool at the Paris La Defense Arena is2.15 meters deep.\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pool\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris La Defense Arena is2.15 meters\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Gymnast refuses to quit Olympics with torn ligament and ends routine crying in pain ArrowMORE:Adam Peaty reveals heart-melting words his son said after missing out on Olympic gold by 0.02 seconds ArrowMORE:Adam Peaty and Holly Ramsay's whirlwind romance as she and his son support him after Olympic win Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4095, \"end\": 4105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 4208, \"end\": 4218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 4223, \"end\": 422